headline: Agilent: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot

headline: Agilent Reports Fourth-Quarter Fiscal Year 2024 Financial Results
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 25, 2024--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today reported revenue of $1.70 billion for the fourth quarter ended October 31, 2024, an increase of 0.8% reported and a decline of 0.3% core(1) compared to the fourth quarter of 2023.

headline: Agilent Announces New Organizational Structure to Support its Market-Focused Strategy
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 25, 2024--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced a new organizational structure to accelerate the company’s operational transformation to drive higher growth through a market-focused, customer-centric enterprise strategy. The new structure, including new leadership roles, takes effect immediately.
